{"description":"Aliru is very present within the Abstract ecosystem, he is an active Gigachad, often there to help the community.

He brings his touch of freshness and originality.

I appreciate him for his authenticity."}

{"description":"KangBokSoon is the legend in Korean Gigachad community. He always on top take care Abstract Korea community in telegram chat and contents on X.

I also have a chance to meet him in Korea durng KBW. SUPER NICE GUY

KangBokSoon is super good energy that people want to be around!"}

{"description":"He is incredibly active on social media defending what he believes in, namely AbstractChain.

His work has been rewarded, as today he is a Gigachad, the Holy Grail of Abstract roles.

I have witnessed his involvement and dedication on the gigachads channel on Abstract; he is helpful, committed, and full of good humor. He's a great guy who is a pleasure to spend time with."}

{"description":"we first talked way like 4 months ago where I only wanted to give him some applause to how his work really means something to the community as we have some of our similar contributions

meanwhile after I'm a part of gigachad, he surprised me even more with how he build personalized leaderboard on top of the ethos to highlight people that are giving out support to others along with how he encourages and reminds to give support to people in abstract community

there are many people who have their own expertise field whether creativity, supportive, consistency, and someone who builds things on top, and guezit0 is one of a few who built"}

{
  "description": "Pavil is well known in the pudgy community for drawing great murals of cultural events and projects like the Gigachads and OnChainHeroes"
}

{
  "description": "I chose not believe in the past that he stole other people's tweets until he did the same to me.

My Article was entirely stolen from top to bottom (theme, phrases, etc.)

He deleted the Article while denying and lying to me that he didn’t steal it, and he didn't try to apologize. And then he slowly came out that he used my Article in chatGPT as an “inspiration” while it was 80% the same.

What makes it worse is that I considered this dude a friend, and he straight lied to me."
}

{
  "description": "Pavil's an amazing OG member of the pudgy community, and his art is electric, always excited to see what he whips up next."
}

{
  "description": "I met sillybilly through onchain heroes. 

sillybilly is an ideal example of what a great community member looks like. his content is great, he shows up and is always positive in the discord/timeline. 

we are very lucky to have him around as a friend"
}

{
  "description": "MIC has been supporting Abstract Chain for a very long time. He always comments and create posts to help promote projects on Abstract.

The consistency is the key of MIC. He is always with Abstract during bull and bear market.

We are so glad to have him!"
}

{
  "description": "One of the very best artists for cutesy style art out there in the space and probably the world. Artist of the lovely chubbicorns. Very unique style, memelord. OG GIF make in this space! Have been frens with him since 2021. Can vouch for his skills and intergrity!"
}

{
  "description": "First time we knew each other though the Huddle, a bit later when i joined Abstract and found out Brian. He is leading Asia region in ecosystem. So warm welcome newbies not only via socials like X, tg, discord, also IRL events (so important). Brian is real legend, happy to support him in such on-chain journey"
}

{
  "description": "Never told with him directly, but what he is doing for a long time deserve huge shout-out. How he cares about his community, early supporters. Nothing more then just huge respect."
}

{
  "description": "My Giga Chad bro in Abstract, OG in Wolves. He always sharing Untamed Reports (pretty helpful) about eco and support others on-chain"
}

{
  "description": "PapaSmooth's been in the Wolves community since day one and he's been one of my favorite members. Very involved, friendly, and happy to share alpha. An asset to any community"
}

{
  "description": "Always delivers: quality, speed, energy. Froggy created artwork for our community that became a favorite and we still use it to this day. He supports, engages, and makes the space better. Stoked we’re in the same crew."
}
